msgid "# `pgroonga_normalize` function"
msgstr "# `pgroonga_normalize`関数"

msgid "Since 2.0.3."
msgstr "2.0.3で追加"

msgid "## Summary"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"`pgroonga_normalize` function converts a text into a normalized form using "
"[Groonga's normalizer modules][groonga-normalizers]."
msgstr ""
"`pgroonga_normalize`関数は[Groongaのノーマライザーモジュール][groonga-"
"normalizers]を使ってテキストをノーマライズします。"

msgid "## Syntax"
msgstr "## 構文"

msgid "Here is the syntax of this function:"
msgstr "この関数の構文は次の通りです。"

msgid ""
"```text\n"
"text pgroonga_normalize(target)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"`target` is a `text` type value to be normalized. By default, it uses the "
"built-in [`NormalizerAuto`][groonga-normalizer-auto] normalizer."
msgstr ""
"`target`はノーマライズ対象となる`text`型の値です。処理にあたっては、デフォル"
"トでは組み込みの[`NormalizerAuto`][groonga-normalizer-auto]ノーマライザーを使"
"います。"

msgid "Here is another syntax of this function:"
msgstr "この関数の別の構文は次の通りです。"

msgid ""
"```text\n"
"text pgroonga_normalize(target, normalizer)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"`normalizer` is a `text` type value which specifies the normalizer module "
"you want to use."
msgstr ""
"`normalizer`は`text`型の値です。使用するノーマライザーモジュールを指定しま"
"す。"

msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使い方"

msgid "You can normalize a `text` type value:"
msgstr "`text`型の値をノーマライズします。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT pgroonga_normalize('aBcDe 123');\n"
"--  pgroonga_normalize \n"
"-- --------------------\n"
"--  abcde 123\n"
"-- (1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "You can specify the normalizer:"
msgstr "ノーマライザーを指定できます。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT pgroonga_command('plugin_register normalizers/mysql');\n"
"SELECT pgroonga_normalize('aBcDe 123', 'NormalizerMySQLGeneralCI');\n"
"--  pgroonga_normalize \n"
"-- --------------------\n"
"--  ABCDE 123\n"
"-- (1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"`plugin_register normalizers/mysql` is needed to use [groonga-normalizer-"
"mysql][groonga-normalizer-mysql]. It provides some MySQL compatible "
"normalizers."
msgstr ""
"[groonga-normalizer-mysql][groonga-normalizer-mysql]を使うために"
"`plugin_register normalizers/mysql`を実行しています。groonga-normalizer-mysql"
"はMySQL互換のノーマライザーを提供します。"

msgid "You can also specify normalizer options:"
msgstr "ノーマライザーのオプションも指定できます。"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT pgroonga_normalize('あア', 'NormalizerNFKC130(\"unify_kana\", "
"true)');\n"
"--  pgroonga_normalize \n"
"-- --------------------\n"
"--  ああ\n"
"-- (1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "You may also specify multiple normalizers. Here is an useless example:"
msgstr ""
"複数のノーマライザーを指定することもできます。以下は実用的ではない例です。\n"

msgid ""
"```sql\n"
"SELECT pgroonga_normalize('あー-ア', \n"
"  '\n"
"    NormalizerNFKC130(\"unify_kana\", true),\n"
"    NormalizerNFKC130(\"unify_hyphen_and_prolonged_sound_mark\", true)\n"
"  '\n"
");\n"
"--  pgroonga_normalize \n"
"-- --------------------\n"
"--  あ--あ\n"
"-- (1 row)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

